; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/cfdisk.md

% cfdisk, linux

# Start the partition manipulator with a specific device
sudo cfdisk <_dev_sdX>

# Create a new partition table for a specific device and manage it
sudo cfdisk <__z___zero_> <_dev_sdX>
